| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-6039 — Recovery Inhibition (ransomcortex)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 941cc16e-5853-55bf-8a4e-cc519ee8e92c"
